Insert the <- assignment operator: Option + - (Mac) or Alt + - (Linux/Windows)

Insert the pipe operator %>%: Type Crtl + Shift + M

Run current line of code: Command + Enter (Mac) or Control + Enter (Linux/Windows)

Comment/uncomment lines: Command + Shift + C (Mac) or Control + Shift + C (Linux/Windows)

Search command history: Command + [up arrow] (Mac) or Control + [up arrow] (Linux/Windows)